# Identity Lifecycle Automation (Okta/Azure AD)

Automate **user onboarding, offboarding, and access updates** from HR data into an Identity Provider (IdP). Ships with a fully working **Mock IdP** so you can run endâ€‘toâ€‘end locally, and pluggable clients for **Okta** and **Azure AD** you can flesh out with real API keys.

---

